        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Stack high-value tiles:</span> DWS doubles EVERYTHING. QUARTZ (Q=10, Z=10) on DWS = 48 points. The more expensive tiles in your word, the bigger the DWS payoff compared to TLS.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">First move advantage:</span> The center star is a DWS. Your opening word is automatically doubled. Start with the highest-scoring word you can form — JINX (36), QUIZ (44), or QUARTZ (48) as openers are devastating.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">TLS + DWS combo:</span> If a word crosses both a TLS and DWS, apply the TLS first (tripling one letter), then double the entire word. Z on TLS within a DWS word = Z scores 30, then the whole word doubles. This is how 80+ point plays happen.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors">
